Create A New Directory : 

Open Github and then Create a 'New Directory' pressing on '+ New' button
Then Give a 'Directory Name' and Description 


Clone Directory:
Copy Directory HTTPS link
Open terminal and goto your target Directory(folder) using      
    cd folder_name
    cd "folder name"
    here cd = change directory
then clone this directory using 
    clone copied_https_url
and Press 'enter'